description:
Danny breaks down this week's Summer House with special guests Paige DeSorbo and Hannah Berner from Bravo's Summer House and The Giggly Squad. They discuss what's to come this season, what's really going on with Kyle and Hannah, and more. After the chat, Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of Atlanta, which featured a Halloween party!


Paige/Hannah Chat: 3:22ish

RHOA Recap: 38:44ish
